# Field list

- company_name — Name of the company.
- use_case_name — Name of the AI use case.
- ai_system_name — Name of the AI system or tool used.
- uses_personal_data — Indicates whether personal data is involved.
- human_review — Indicates whether a human reviews or approves the output.
- risk_level — Overall risk assessment level.
- recommended_measures — Suggested governance actions or next steps.

